    <p>The paving industry generates over <strong>$100 billion in revenue annually</strong>. With the right local SEO strategy, local paving contractors can reach the first page of Google local results within 30 days — the timeline for local results is faster than most contractors expect, which makes the front-loaded investment in getting the strategy right particularly valuable.</p>

