    <p>In less competitive trades, the map pack positions are more accessible. Bay Area trades where Oakland profiles are inconsistently managed — specialty electrical work, masonry, custom carpentry — can see meaningful map pack movement in 60 to 90 days with a properly structured profile. The key is identifying where the real competition level sits before planning investment, rather than assuming every Oakland trade is equally contested.</p>

