    <p>Every Bay Area city the plumber serves should have an emergency plumbing city page — not just a general plumbing city page. "Emergency Plumber San Jose," "Emergency Plumber Oakland," "Emergency Plumber Palo Alto" are each separate searches with separate map pack results. The contractors appearing in those results have pages specifically targeting those terms. A contractor with only a generic "plumbing services" city page is not competing with the same authority as one who has built the emergency-specific structure.</p>

