    <p>The most efficient path into the San Jose map pack for a new entrant is the neighborhood-level approach: build dedicated pages for San Jose's five to eight highest-demand neighborhoods, acquire reviews that mention those neighborhood names, and use neighborhood-specific Google Posts to build geographic authority in the GBP. This produces neighborhood-level map pack appearances within three to four months, which compound into city-level authority over the following six to eight months.</p>

